                <ul class="list-unstyled">
                    <li>
                        <p><i class="bi bi-check2-circle color"></i>  Assessment of Current Systems: Begin by thoroughly assessing your existing systems and identifying which ones need to be integrated with Dynamics 365 for a seamless data flow.</p>
                    </li>
