                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p><i class="bi bi-check2-circle color"></i>  Test Integration in Phases: Start with small, non-critical integrations to test connectivity, data integrity, and functionality before scaling up to more complex processes.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
